# <type>[(scope)][!]: <description>
#
# [optional body]
#
# [optional footer(s)]
#
# ┌── Types: ────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │   feat      New feature                    (minor bump)  │
# │   fix       Bug fix                        (patch bump)  │
# │   perf      Performance improvement                      │
# │   security  Security fix or hardening                    │
# │   refactor  Code restructuring (no behavior change)      │
# │   doc       Documentation only                           │
# │   docs      Documentation only                           │
# │   style     Formatting, whitespace (no code change)      │
# │   test      Adding or updating tests                     │
# │   chore     Build, CI, tooling, dependencies             │
# │   revert    Revert a previous commit                     │
# │   remove    Remove feature or code                       │
# │   build     Build system changes (skipped in changelog)  │
# │   ci        CI configuration (skipped in changelog)      │
# │   devops    DevOps changes (synonym for ci)              │
# └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
#
# Breaking changes: add ! after the type/scope:
#   refactor!: rewrite matching engine
#   feat(api)!: change return type
#
# Footers:
#   Fixes #123
#   Closes #123
#   Refs #456
#
# Examples:
#   feat(glob): add character class negation [^abc]
#   fix: prevent stack overflow on deeply nested patterns
#   chore: update BenchmarkDotNet to 0.14.0
#   docs: add DEVELOPER_WORKFLOW.md
